01:55.549 --> 01:57.385
oh, somebody's at my door.

01:57.418 --> 01:59.720
ok, later.
i'll tell you how it goes.

02:03.924 --> 02:08.461
oh. didn't i say i'd
meet you at flookie's?

02:08.496 --> 02:12.366
i thought, just as easy,
i'd pick you up.

02:12.400 --> 02:14.435
i was thinking
about you.

02:18.372 --> 02:21.542
oh, my god, billy.
it's beautiful.

02:24.678 --> 02:34.355
* 'cause i'm stormy

02:36.357 --> 02:38.826
* yes, i'm stormy...

02:38.859 --> 02:40.528
hmm. not now.

02:40.561 --> 02:43.797
i can't help myself.
your body's so perfect.

02:43.831 --> 02:46.434
what if somebody
comes in?

02:48.302 --> 02:49.403
let's go up.

02:49.437 --> 02:51.405
it's too hot upstairs.

02:51.439 --> 02:53.374
oh, no, no, no.
just to lay down.

02:53.407 --> 02:54.742
my room's
a disaster.

02:54.775 --> 02:57.278
we're not going
to take everything
off, just snuggle.

02:57.311 --> 02:59.847
no! let's just go
ahead to flookie's

02:59.880 --> 03:01.415
and meet the others.

03:01.449 --> 03:03.784
no, come on.
five minutes.

03:03.817 --> 03:08.356
singer: * with
your blood-soaked lips *

03:08.389 --> 03:11.792
* whet my appetite...

03:11.825 --> 03:14.662
my pictures, my poems.
why'd you take 'em down?

03:14.695 --> 03:16.264
why are they
in a box?

03:16.297 --> 03:17.598
this disgusting
color.

03:17.631 --> 03:18.999
my dad said
he'd repaint

03:19.032 --> 03:20.934
if i cleared
everything.

03:25.773 --> 03:28.509
you know, you're not
a very good liar.

03:28.542 --> 03:29.943
i didn't lie.

03:29.977 --> 03:32.446
get off,
get off!

03:32.480 --> 03:33.647
get out!

03:33.681 --> 03:35.283
wait!

03:36.784 --> 03:38.952
oh, i'm not good enough
for you anymore?

03:38.986 --> 03:40.721
i bet if my name
was kevin shane...

03:40.754 --> 03:43.757
what's kevin shane
got to do with it?

03:43.791 --> 03:47.961
because i don't drive
a four-by like him!

03:47.995 --> 03:49.363
get out!

03:49.397 --> 03:50.531
i'm talking to you.

03:50.564 --> 03:51.699
not in that tone
you don't.

03:51.732 --> 03:54.402
erin, if you
don't love me,

03:54.435 --> 03:56.404
why did you make
love to me?

03:56.437 --> 03:57.805
you're the one

03:57.838 --> 04:00.808
that made it into
this big serious thing.

04:01.775 --> 04:02.843
all lies, right?

04:02.876 --> 04:05.012
i didn't lie.
shut up.

04:05.045 --> 04:07.014
don't tell me
to shut up!

04:07.047 --> 04:09.016
get out, you idiot.
i'm calling the police.

04:09.049 --> 04:10.751
don't you ever
call me an idiot.

04:10.784 --> 04:12.386
i'm calling the police.
no!

04:12.420 --> 04:14.688
stop it! let go!

04:15.989 --> 04:22.363
singer:
* 'cause i'm stormy

04:22.396 --> 04:24.264
* again

04:26.700 --> 04:32.906
* 'cause i'm stormy

