world to know.

01:20:08.604 --> 01:20:10.006
no! let go!

01:20:10.039 --> 01:20:12.241
no! no!

01:20:12.275 --> 01:20:15.144
let go! no! let go!

01:20:15.178 --> 01:20:16.846
no! no!

01:20:35.298 --> 01:20:37.266
laurel!

01:20:37.300 --> 01:20:39.002
